# Simulation Iterators

> Standard library simulation iterators.

<section class="usage">

## Usage

```javascript
var ns = require( '@stdlib/simulate/iter' );
```

#### ns

Standard library simulation iterators.

```javascript
var iterators = ns;
// returns {...}
```
